Program: Outlook
Title: The Deserts of the World
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrkn
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Travel writer Martin Buckley talks about his desert journeys. Also, Desert enthusiasts around the world talk about why they love deserts. A visit to Wadi Elrayan oasis in Egypt. Water supply and the greening of the Negev Desert by Israel. Presenter: Frederick Dove.